],"Web Development"]}],["$","h1",null,{"className":"mt-3 font-display font-semibold text-4xl md:text-6xl tracking-tight text-ink-50","children":"Core Web Vitals: Why UK B2B Sites Score Worse Than US Equivalents"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-5 text-lg text-ink-300","children":"British marketing sites consistently fail Core Web Vitals at higher rates than US peers. We dug into 200 .co.uk sites and identified the five recurring causes — and how to fix them."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-7 flex items-center gap-3","children":["$","$L6",null,{"href":"/blog/author/theo-ember","className":"flex items-center gap-3 group","aria-label":"More posts by Theo Ember","children":[["$","$L7",null,{"src":"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500648767791-00dcc994a43e?auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&q=80","alt":"","width":44,"height":44,"className":"rounded-full border border-ink-700"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"text-sm","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"font-semibold text-ink-50 group-hover:text-ember-600 transition-colors","children":"Theo Ember"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"text-ink-400","children":[["$","time",null,{"dateTime":"2026-03-30","children":"29 March 2026"}],["$","span",null,{"aria-hidden":true,"children":" · "}],["$","span",null,{"children":[9," min read"]}],[" · Updated ",["$","time",null,{"dateTime":"2026-05-04","children":"3 May 2026"}]]]}]]}]]}]}]]}]]}]]}]
22:["$","section",null,{"className":"bg-white","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"container-x","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"relative aspect-[16/8] overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-ink-700 shadow-lift","children":["$","$L7",null,{"src":"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551434678-e076c223a692?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1800&q=80","alt":"Developer reviewing performance metrics on multiple monitors","fill":true,"priority":true,"sizes":"(min-width: 1024px) 80vw, 100vw","className":"object-cover"}]}]}]}]
23:["$","section",null,{"className":"bg-white pt-16 pb-24","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"container-x grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_260px]","children":[["$","article",null,{"data-progress-target":true,"className":"max-w-3xl prose-base","children":[[["$","p","0",{"className":"text-ink-200 text-lg leading-relaxed mt-6","children":"We ran a Chrome User Experience Report (CrUX) pull across 200 .co.uk B2B marketing sites in financial services, professional services, and SaaS, and benchmarked them against 200 US peers of similar revenue. The UK cohort was slower on every metric: 14% worse on LCP, 22% worse on INP, 9% worse on CLS. The gap isn't because British developers are worse. It's structural — and most of it is fixable in a sprint."}],["$","h2","1",{"id":"cause-1-cookie-banners","className":"font-display font-semibold text-2xl md:text-3xl text-ink-50 mt-14 scroll-mt-24 group","children":["$","a",null,{"href":"#cause-1-cookie-banners","className":"no-underline","children":[["$","span",null,{"children":"Cause 1: Cookie banners that block the main thread"}],["$","span",null,{"aria-hidden":true,"className":"ml-2 text-ember-500/0 group-hover:text-ember-500/80 transition-colors text-base","children":"#"}]]}]}],["$","p","2",{"className":"text-ink-200 text-lg leading-relaxed mt-6","children":"UK GDPR compliance pressure has pushed most British sites onto third-party Consent Management Platforms (CMPs) — OneTrust, Cookiebot, Iubenda. These products are heavy: 80–250KB of JavaScript that runs before the page settles. They're the single biggest contributor to poor INP scores in our dataset."}],["$","p","3",{"className":"text-ink-200 text-lg leading-relaxed mt-6","children":"The fix isn't to remove the banner — it's to defer the CMP's analytics tag firing until after first input. Most CMPs support an async-first config; almost no one ships it. Move it to the bottom of the body, mark it defer, and gate non-essential script firing behind requestIdleCallback. We routinely shave 200–400ms off INP with this single change."}],["$","h2","4",{"id":"cause-2-fonts","className":"font-display font-semibold text-2xl md:text-3xl text-ink-50 mt-14 scroll-mt-24 group","children":["$","a",null,{"href":"#cause-2-fonts","className":"no-underline","children":[["$","span",null,{"children":"Cause 2: Custom fonts loaded from Adobe Fonts (Typekit)"}],["$","span",null,{"aria-hidden":true,"className":"ml-2 text-ember-500/0 group-hover:text-ember-500/80 transition-colors text-base","children":"#"}]]}]}],["$","p","5",{"className":"text-ink-200 text-lg leading-relaxed mt-6","children":"UK design-led brands disproportionately use Adobe Fonts via Typekit. Typekit requires a render-blocking CSS request to use.typekit.net, which sits on a CDN that's slower from UK ISPs than the equivalent Google Fonts hop. The result is a 200–600ms LCP penalty on first paint."}],["$","ul","6",{"className":"mt-6 space-y-3","children":[["$","li","0",{"className":"flex items-start gap-3 text-ink-200 text-lg leading-relaxed","children":[["$","span",null,{"aria-hidden":true,"className":"mt-2.5 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-ember-500 shrink-0"}],["$","span",null,{"children":"Switch to self-hosted woff2 with font-display: swap."}]]}],["$","li","1",{"className":"flex items-start gap-3 text-ink-200 text-lg leading-relaxed","children":[["$","span",null,{"aria-hidden":true,"className":"mt-2.5 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-ember-500 shrink-0"}],["$","span",null,{"children":"Preload only the two weights used above the fold."}]]}],["$","li","2",{"className":"flex items-start gap-3 text-ink-200 text-lg leading-relaxed","children":[["$","span",null,{"aria-hidden":true,"className":"mt-2.5 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-ember-500 shrink-0"}],"$L26"]}]]}],"$L27","$L28","$L29","$L2a","$L2b","$L2c","$L2d","$L2e","$L2f","$L30"],"$L31","$L32","$L33","$L34"]}],"$L35"]}]}]
